# Force LF line endings for all text files across all platforms.
# Without this, Windows CI checkout applies CRLF and Prettier's format:check
# fails on 30+ files while Ubuntu / macOS pass. See CI runs on PR #5.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types (avoid auto-detection surprises).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
